name: detailed-guidance-documentation-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for structuring detailed guidance Markdown documents
globs: "*.md"

- Use a clear title for the function/component to be implemented
- Provide a brief description of the function
- List components that need to be implemented
- Specify functional requirements the feature must meet
- Define constraints or rules to follow
- Include references to related documents
- Outline criteria for task completion 